reviewText:
This video left me on the floor prostrate before God.

If you need a renewing or refreshing, this video is definitely a must see and a must have.

This is defitnately well needed for all man kind. Juanita as always tells it like it is. If you've lost the fire you had for God, if you have forgotten who comes first in all things, and if you need to know if you just like or love Jesus you will know after looking at this tape. I recommend this to people who are serious about running and living for the Lord Jesus Christ.
